<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>DADI Documentation</title>

    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
    <meta name="copyright" content="{@formatDate unix=global.timestamp format="YYYY" /}">
    <meta name="description" content="{global.description}">

    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Muli:400,400i,900" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/styles.css">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/logo.png">

    <script type="text/javascript" src="/scripts.js"></script>

  </head>
<body>

<nav>
  <ul>
    <li><a class="active" href="#introduction">Introduction</a></li>
  </ul>
  <ul>
    {#navigation}
      <li><a href="#app-{id}">{name}</a>
        {@markdown}{map}{/markdown}
      </li>
    {/navigation}
  </ul>
</nav>

<main>

<header>
  <a href="/">
    <img src="https://dadi.tech/assets/img/dadi-colour.svg" width="150" height="35" alt="DADI" class="logo">
  </a>

  <div class="search">
    <input type="search" placeholder="Search the documentation…">
  </div>
</header>

<div class="intro" id="introduction">
  <h2><a id="introduction" class="anchor" href="#introduction"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="icon icon-link" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>Documentation</h2>

  <p class="medium">DADI is a modern microservices framework, built specifically in support of the principles of API first and COPE.</p>

  <p class="small"><a href="#" class="btn">More about DADI</a> <a href="#" class="btn">Chat with our devs</a></p>

  <div class="intro__feat">
    <div>
      <img src="https://dadi.tech/assets/icons/database.svg">
      <h3>API-first and COPE</h3>
      <p>Connects your content to everything: drive multiple products from a single editorial workflow.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <img src="https://dadi.tech/assets/icons/secure.svg">
      <h3>Open source</h3>
      <p>Dive in and use straight away: enterprise muscle without the fat – or the greedy licence fees.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <img src="https://dadi.tech/assets/icons/colors.svg">
      <h3>Microservices technology</h3>
      <p>A platform built as small, independent processes enabling flexibility and high performance.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{#docs.results}
  <div class="docs docs--{attributes._id}">
    <h1 id="app-{attributes._id}">{attributes.title}</h1>
    {@markdown app=attributes._id}{contentText|s}{/markdown}
  </div>
{/docs.results}

</main>

{! <footer>
  &#x26A1; Powered by <a href="https://dadi.tech/platform/web">DADI Web {version}</a><br>© {@formatDate unix=global.timestamp format="YYYY" /}
</footer> !}


</body>
</html>